Plot.
From a riddle-speaking butterfly, a unicorn learns that she is supposedly 
the last of her kind, all the others having been herded away by the Red 
Bull. The unicorn sets out to discover the truth behind the butterfly's 
words. She is eventually joined on her quest by Schmendrick, a second-rate 
magician, and Molly Grue, a now middle-aged woman who dreamed all her 
life of seeing a unicorn. Their journey leads them far from home, all 
the way to the castle of King Haggard.
